diverse_sailfish.en: The community is showing how diverse Sailfish OS can be with photos of their Sailfish experiences.

javascript_functionality.ar: الجافاسكربت -JavaScript- يستخدم لـTwitter API و لوظائف موقعنا الخاصة.
javascript_functionality.cs: Používáme JavaScript, kvůli Twitter API a dalším funkcím našeho webu.
javascript_functionality.en: JavaScript is used for the Twitter API and our own site functionality.
javascript_functionality.es: JavaScript se utiliza para la API de Twitter y el funcionamiento de nuestro propio sitio.
javascript_functionality.it: JavaScript viene usato per l'API di Twitter e per funzionalità del nostro stesso sito.
javascript_functionality.ru: JavaScript используется для API Твиттера и функционирования нашего сайта
javascript_functionality.sl: JavaScript je uporabljen za Twitter-jev programski vmesnik in delovanje naše spletne strani.
javascript_functionality.sr: JavaScript се користи за Твитеров програмски интерфејс и рад нашег сајта.
javascript_functionality.sr-latin: JavaScript se koristi za Twitter programski interfejs i rad našeg sajta.

noscript_detected.ar: لاحظت أنك تستخدم noscript أو  أنك لم تمكن الجافاسكربت-JS. هل من الممكن تمكين الجافاسكربت-JS-على هذا الموقع؟
noscript_detected.cs: Vypadá to, že používáte noscript nebo je JS deaktivovaný. Co třeba zapnout JS pro tento web?
noscript_detected.en: I see you're using noscript or have JS disabled. Mind enabling JS for this site?
noscript_detected.es: Veo que estás usando noscript o tienes JS deshabilitado. ¿Te importaría activar JS para este sitio?
noscript_detected.it: Vedo che stai usando noscript o che hai disabilitato i JS. Ti spiacerebbe attivare i JS per questo sito?
noscript_detected.ru: Видимо, Вы используете noscript или отключили JavaScript. Не могли бы Вы включить JS для этого сайта?
noscript_detected.sl: Vidimo, da uporabljate noscript ali pa imate JavaScript onemogočen. Bi lahko, prosim omogočili JavaScript za to stran?
noscript_detected.sr: Видимо да користите noscript или вам је JavaScript онемогућен. Да ли бисте били љубазни да омогућите JavaScript за овај сајт?
noscript_detected.sr-latin: Vidimo da koristite noscript ili vam je JavaScript onemogućen. Da li biste bili ljubazni da omogućite JavaScript za ovaj sajt?

sailor_feed_messages.en: Below are kind remarks from around the world by the community. Get yours added by tweeting with the hashtag #ISupportJolla.

screenshots_sailfishosexperience.en: Below are some screenshots taken by users, showing off their Sailfish OS experience! Get yours added by using #SailfishOSExperience on Twitter.

interest_fellow_fans.en: If you're interested in taking to fellow fans, we welcome you to join the unofficial Sailfish OS Fan Club on Telegram.

interest_official.en: If you want to learn about official ways of joining the dicussion and getting involved, head over to SailfishOS.org's Community page.

vibrant_community_message.en: The Sailfish OS community is vibrant, full of developers, users, and fans alike.
